Text:
I'M THE GUY WHO CAN GET IT
FOR YA-- CIGARETTES; A BAG OF
REEFER, IF THAT'S YOUR THING;

IF IT WAS A TOOTHBRUSH,
I WOULDN'T ASK QUESTIONS;
I'D JUST QUOTE A PRICE.

YOU DONE BROKE HIS NOSE;
HE OUGHTA HAVE SOMETHING
TO SHOW FOR IT.

PLAYING CARDS
WITH NAKED LADIES ON 'EM;
YOU NAME IT.

IN HERE
HE'S AN IMPORTANT MAN;
HE'S AN EDUCATED MAN.
